"-----------------------------------------------------------------
" plugin - incsearch
" We don't need set basic usage here, because above easymotion
" already integrated it.
" Brant: Comment out "map /", because it will invalid C-v for pasting to /
"-----------------------------------------------------------------
" map /  <Plug>(incsearch-forward)
